question.en:
In MVCC, when Transaction A updates a row and Transaction B reads it before A commits, what does B see?
```sql
-- Transaction A
BEGIN;
UPDATE users SET name = 'Alice' WHERE id = 1;
-- Transaction B (concurrent, started before A's UPDATE)
SELECT name FROM users WHERE id = 1;
```

question.ru:
